(12093, 'aviation_email_final_questionnaire', '<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="http://www.cjaviationsafety.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/cert_header2.jpg" alt="cert_header2" width="600" height="86" />\r\n<div style="width: 100%; padding-top: 50px;">\r\n<h1 style="background-color: #05519c; padding: 15px; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0;">User Final Questionnaire</h1>\r\n<div style="background-color: #bedbf4; padding: 15px; min-height: 200px; font-size: 14px;">Hello,{user} has answered on the final questionnaire.\r\n\r\n<p>Here are the results:</p>\r\n<h4>CBT Delivery & Methods  (How would you rate the following)? </h4>\r\n<p>The CBT stimulated interest - <b>{radio_answer_01}</b></p>\r\n<p>Standard of CBT delivery - <b>{radio_answer_02}</b></p>\r\n<p>Effective interaction and participation of CBT - <b>{radio_answer_03}</b></p>\r\n<p>Effectiveness of the questions - <b>{radio_answer_04}</b></p>\r\n<p>Delivery and methods used - <b>{radio_answer_05}</b></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Course Objective & Course Content (How would you rate the following)</h4>\r\n<p>The course met your personal objectives - <b>{radio_answer_06}</b></p>\r\n<p>Understanding of Human factors and Performance Limitations - <b>{radio_answer_07}</b></p>\r\n<p>How well do you understand how to report hazards, errors and improvements - <b>{radio_answer_08}</b></p>\r\n<p>Understanding the company error management programme - <b>{radio_answer_09}</b></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Course Notes & Hand-outs  (How would you rate the following)?</h4>\r\n<p>Quality of Presentation - <b>{radio_answer_10}</b></p>\r\n<p>Quality of supporting course documentation - <b>{radio_answer_11}</b></p>\r\n<p>Course material & training aids - <b>{radio_answer_12}</b></p>\r\n<p>How would you rate the following? - <b>{radio_answer_13}</b></p>\r\n<p>Overall assessment of the course - <b>{radio_answer_14}</b></p>\r\n\r\n<h4> What do you think you could have done (if anything) to get more out of this course </h4>\r\n<p><b>{textarea_answer_15}</b></p>\r\n\r\n<h4> What do you think you have gained from this course? </h4>\r\n<p><b>{textarea_answer_16}</b></p>\r\n\r\n<h4> Following this course will you change your attitudes/behaviours with regards to your daily role? </h4>\r\n<p><b>{textarea_answer_17}</b></p>\r\n\r\n<h4> Do you believe you work in an environment which embraces a Just Culture and encourages reporting? If no, why?</h4>\r\n<p><b>{textarea_answer_18}</b></p>\r\n\r\n<h4> Do you now feel empowered to submit a report? If no, why? </h4>\r\n<p><b>{textarea_answer_19}</b></p>\r\n\r\n<h4> Do you feel your submission will be dealt with appropriately? If no, why? </h4>\r\n<p><b>{textarea_answer_20}</b></p>\r\n\r\n<h4> Please use the space below to add any other comments or improvements regarding the CBT course. </h4>\r\n<p><b>{textarea_answer_21}</b></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h4 style="background-color: #05519c; padding: 15px; color: #fff; margin-top: 0;">Copyright to CJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited 2014</h4>\r\n</div>', 'yes'),
