(5, 1, '2014-11-03 15:33:33', '2014-11-03 15:33:33', '[row]\r\n\r\n[column_5]\r\n<h1>Welcome</h1>\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent ac turpis lorem. Praesent molestie metus auctor, scelerisque nisi id, consectetur urna. Aliquam faucibus orci sit amet leo imperdiet eleifend sed ac magna. Nulla quis libero sagittis, malesuada mi sed, egestas ligula. Morbi nunc mi, suscipit vel semper id, dignissim et quam. Etiam ut nunc nibh. Pellentesque pulvinar ex massa, et varius mauris eleifend ut.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1>Contact me</h1>\r\nOffice: xxx\r\n\r\nEmail: xxx\r\n\r\nOr leave a message <a title="Contact Us" href="http://localhost/aviation-safety/contact-us/">here</a>\r\n\r\n[/column_5]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[column_5]\r\n<div class="home_login">\r\n<h1>CBT Login</h1>\r\nPlease log into the CBT website bellow, make sure you have the correct username and password.\r\n\r\n[wppb-login redirect="http://localhost/aviation-safety/user-dashboard"]\r\n[wppb-register]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h1>News</h1>\r\n[news-widget]\r\n\r\n[/column_5]\r\n\r\n[/row]', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2015-02-24 11:08:18', '2015-02-24 11:08:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/aviation-safety/?page_id=5', 0, 'page', '', 0),
