(69, 1, '2014-11-13 09:10:56', '2014-11-13 09:10:56', '\r\n<h1>CJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited</h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5>All Data contained within this document is âCJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited IPRâ</h5>\r\n[row]\r\n[column_6]\r\n<h4>This is an unpublished work created in 2014, All rights reserved.</h4>\r\n[avatar]The information contained in this document/record is proprietary to CJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited unless stated otherwise and is made available in confidence; it must not be used or disclosed without the express written permission of CJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited which may be given by contract. This document/record may not be reproduced in whole or in part in any form without the express written consent of CJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited[/avatar]\r\n\r\nAny changes made to this document by the Authority or by any third party may affect ownership of the copyright therein, which ordinarily vests in CJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited . Furthermore, CJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited shall not be held liable or responsible for any such changes that have not been approved or underwritten by CJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited in accordance with the above contract.\r\n[/column_6]\r\n[column_6]\r\n<h4>Public Access: Freedom Of Information Act 2000, etc.</h4>\r\nThis document contains commercially-sensitive trade secrets and commercial information as of the date provided to the original recipient by CJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited and is provided in confidence. Following a request for this information, public authorities should consult with CJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited, regarding the current releasability of the information prior to the decision to release all or part of this document, and in any event are to notify CJ Aviation Safety Consultancy Limited prior to any release. Release of this information by a public authority may constitute an actionable breach of confidence.\r\n[/column_6]\r\n[/row]', 'Slide 01 - Copyright', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'slide-01-copyright', '', '', '2015-02-11 07:46:58', '2015-02-11 07:46:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/aviation-safety/?post_type=aviation-questions&#038;p=69', 0, 'aviation-questions', '', 0),
