(163, 1, '2015-02-16 15:44:26', '2015-02-16 15:44:26', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">\n	"Human Factors" refers to the study of human \n	<span class="tooltips">capabilities\n		<span> \n			<a class="yellow_text">capability</a>\n			<br /> noun<br /> the power or ability to do something.<br />\n			"he had an intuitive capability of bringing the best out in people"<br />\n		</span>\n	</span>\nand limitations in the workplace.</h2>\n\n<h2>\n[row]\n\n[column_6]\n\n<img class="size-full wp-image-162 alignright" src="http://localhost/aviation-safety/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/slide_09-a.png" alt="slide_09-a" width="335" height="244" />\n\n[/column_6]\n\n[column_6]\n\n<img class="size-full wp-image-164 alignleft" src="http://localhost/aviation-safety/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/slide_09-b.png" alt="slide_09-b" width="327" height="245" />\n\n[/column_6]\n\n[/row]', 'Slide 09 - HUMAN PERFORMANCE AND ABILITIES', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '77-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-02-16 15:44:26', '2015-02-16 15:44:26', '', 77, 'http://localhost/aviation-safety/77-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
