(311, 1, '2015-02-25 15:37:56', '2015-02-25 15:37:56', '<h2>CBT TRAINING EVALUATION SHEET</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We are always keen to receive your views on the training we deliver. The feedback you give allows us to continually adapt training to better suit your needs. We would appreciate it if you could spend a few minutes filling in this form. </p>\r\n<p>All feedback will be treated in the strictest of confidence.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="question_option">\r\n<table>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class="al_left">\r\nCBT Delivery & Methods\r\n(How would you rate the following)?\r\n</th>\r\n<th>Very Good</th>\r\n<th>Good</th>\r\n<th>Satisfactory</th>\r\n<th>Poor</th>\r\n<th>Very Poor</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="al_left">The CBT stimulated interest</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<input id="finals_01_01" class="radio_answer" type="radio" value="Very Good" name="radio_answer_01"><label for="finals_01_01"><span></span></label>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<input id="finals_01_02" class="radio_answer" type="radio" value="Good" name="radio_answer_01"><label for="finals_01_02"><span></span></label>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<input id="finals_01_03" class="radio_answer" type="radio" value="Satisfactory" name="radio_answer_01"><label for="finals_01_03"><span></span></label>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<input id="finals_01_04" class="radio_answer" type="radio" value="Poor" name="radio_answer_01"><label for="finals_01_04"><span></span></label>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<input id="finals_01_05" class="radio_answer" type="radio" value="Very  Poor" name="radio_answer_01"><label for="finals_01_05"><span></span></label>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="al_left">Standard of  CBT delivery</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<input id="finals_02_01" class="radio_answer" type="radio" value="Very Good" name="radio_answer_02"><label for="finals_02_01"><span></span></label>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<input id="finals_02_02" class="radio_answer" type="radio" value="Good" name="radio_answer_02"><label for="finals_02_02"><span></span></label>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r