ft" colspan="6">\nFollowing this course will you change your attitudes/behaviours with regards to your daily role?\n</th>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td colspan="6" class="spaceme ">\n<textarea name="textarea_answer_17" id="textarea_answer_17"></textarea>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th class="al_left" colspan="6">\nDo you believe you work in an environment which embraces a Just Culture and encourages reporting? If no, why?</th>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td colspan="6" class="spaceme ">\n<textarea name="textarea_answer_18" id="textarea_answer_18"></textarea>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th class="al_left" colspan="6">\nDo you now feel empowered to submit a report? If no, why?\n</th>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td colspan="6" class="spaceme ">\n<textarea name="textarea_answer_19" id="textarea_answer_19"></textarea>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th class="al_left" colspan="6">\nDo you feel your submission will be dealt with appropriately? If no, why?\n</th>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td colspan="6" class="spaceme ">\n<textarea name="textarea_answer_20" id="textarea_answer_20"></textarea>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th class="al_left" colspan="5">\nPlease use the space below to add any other comments or improvements regarding the CBT course.\n</th>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td colspan="5" class="spaceme ">\n<textarea name="textarea_answer_21" id="textarea_answer_21"></textarea>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<a class="button" href="javascript: void(0);" id="send_answers">Submit</a>', 'Slide Questionnaire', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '311-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-02-25 16:35:30', '2015-02-25 16:35:30', '', 311, 'http://localhost/aviation-safety/311-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
